column8: Partly cloudy. The chance of fog in the early morning. Light winds becoming southeast to southwesterly 15 to 25 km/h in the middle of the day then becoming light in the late evening.
Partly cloudy. The chance of morning fog. Light winds becoming northerly 15 to 25 km/h during the day.
Cloudy. Medium (50%) chance of showers, most likely in the morning. Winds north to northwesterly 15 to 25 km/h shifting south to southeasterly during the morning.
Partly cloudy. Slight (30%) chance of a shower, most likely later in the day. Winds northeast to southeasterly 15 to 20 km/h tending northwest to northeasterly 15 to 25 km/h during the morning.
Partly cloudy. Medium (50%) chance of showers. Winds north to northeasterly 15 to 25 km/h tending north to northwesterly 20 to 30 km/h during the morning.
Cloudy. Medium (50%) chance of showers. Winds northeast to southeasterly 15 to 20 km/h tending south to southeasterly 25 to 35 km/h during the morning.
